## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates how I deployed a web server using Nginx on a Linux-based EC2 instance. The goal was to understand server provisioning, service management, and basic networking concepts.

### 🏗️ Environment
- Cloud Provider: AWS EC2
- Operating System: Ubuntu
- Web Server: Nginx
- Access Method: SSH

### 🎯 Objectives
- Launch a cloud server
- Install and configure Nginx
- Access the server via browser
- Verify web server functionality
